    1.2  "Authorized Use" means operation of the Software solely for Licensee's internal business purposes, in object‑code form, on the hardware and for the number of users or instances specified in any applicable order, invoice, or other ordering document ("Order").

2.  OWNERSHIP AND INTELLECTUAL PROPERTY
